********************************************************************************

Automated install is complete. There are a few steps that need to be completed
manually.

 1) Launch dropbox and login - get the sync started
 2) Change the launch key for Alfred to CTRL-SPACE
 3) Setup gmail and fastmail in Mail.app
 4) System Preferences -> Security & Privacy -> Privacy, enable Slate & Karabiner
 5) Set Slate to launch on login
 6) Set Karabiner to launch on login
 7) Once dropbox is synced, launch 1Password & set up sync to dropbox
 8) Launch Chrome, login, and let it link to 1Password
 9) Launch Safari and let it link to 1Password
10) Launch nvALT and start sycing to Simplenote
11) Login to spotify

* Alfred powerpack
* install app store apps
* set up hyper key mappings as they occur to me with keyboard maestro
* enable install of apps from anywhere
* set computer name
* setup favorites in finder
